text: Pádraig Hampsey is a Gaelic football player who plays at inter-county level for Tyrone. At club level he plays for Coalisland. He started at corner-back for Tyrone in the 2018 All-Ireland Final defeat to Dublin. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Tyrone inter-county Gaelic footballers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
